      "options": {
        "content": "## 📧 Email Cascade RCA — Live Spike\n\nLanding page for the *“show me every email I have ever sent”* demo. The agent fans 2000 hourly tool calls + 2000 LLM summarizer calls when a user asks for an unbounded mailbox dump. Watch:\n\n1. **Top conversations by agent calls/min** — your live ask spikes to the top within seconds.\n2. **Tokens/sec + $/sec** — cost climbs in real time.\n3. **Alert state** — the *Conv runaway* alert fires above 1k tokens/sec/conv.\n4. **Email sent** — webhook-receiver emits an `email_sent` log line when the alert routes notification.\n5. **Live cascade tail** — every per-chunk probe + summarize call, scrolling.\n\nDemo flow: type the trigger phrase → watch the right column light up → click trace → see all 2000 nested spans in Tempo.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
