        "content": "### 🔍 Pivot to the trace\n\nGrab the conv_id from the **Top 10 conversations** panel above, then jump to **Tempo → Search** and use:\n\n```\n{ resource.service.name = \"acme-bot-api\" && conv_id = \"<paste>\" }\n```\n\nYou'll see the cascade as one big root span with 2000 nested children. The pre-2018 chunks finish in ~5ms each (empty fast); post-2018 chunks fan out to `suggested-reply-writer` for the LLM summarize. Total span count on the trace: ~2059 (1 root + 1 attempt-1 + 10 attempt-2 + 2000 attempt-3 + 48 summarizers + judges + tools).",
